Body: Description: Please confirm that the e-mail address for jspidcock@pidcockcompany.com will no longer receive any e-mail alerts from Endpoint Protector. I thought I removed this account from the administrators however it was reported that alert e-mails were still being received.
What We've Learned Updated: Admin has been removed +  asked customer to delete the alerts and re-create them and if the issue still persists after that.
Next Steps Updated: Waiting on customer feedback.
